CTY1S.HE.summary: Citycon Oyj, a real estate investment company, owns, develops, and manages retail, office space, and housing properties in the Nordic region. The company owns 40 centers and 1 other retail property. Citycon Oyj was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in Espoo, Finland.
